## 📐 Design Philosophy & Standards
This codebase adheres to the following structural patterns and development practices:
- **Clean Architecture & Separation of Concerns:** Core business logic is strictly decoupled from request-routing entry points and database interfaces.
- **Robust Exception Management:** Exception handling decorators or middleware are leveraged to guarantee system stability.
- **AST-Backed Verification:** Static analysis rules verify system integrity and prevent architectural regression.

